statements: SELECT user_id, interaction_time, interaction_type, environment_type FROM user_interaction_logs;
SELECT interaction_type, user_id FROM user_interaction_logs;
SELECT interaction_time, user_id, environment_type FROM user_interaction_logs;
SELECT * FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT interaction_type, interaction_time FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE environment_type = 'production';
SELECT user_id, interaction_time, interaction_type, environment_type FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY interaction_time DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE environment_type = 'Production' AND interaction_type LIKE '%click%' ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE user_id = 2 AND environment_type IN ('Development', 'Staging') ORDER BY interaction_time ASC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM user_interaction_logs GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_interactions > 5 ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;
SELECT user_id, MAX(interaction_time) AS last_interaction FROM user_interaction_logs GROUP BY user_id HAVING last_interaction >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE user_id = 10;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE interaction_time > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY interaction_time DESC;
SELECT interaction_data->>'status' AS status, interaction_type FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE user_id = 5 ORDER BY interaction_time ASC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM user_interaction_logs GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 10;
SELECT MAX(interaction_time) AS latest_interaction_time, MIN(interaction_time) AS earliest_interaction_time FROM user_interaction_logs;
SELECT * FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE user_id = 101 ORDER BY interaction_time DESC;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, interaction_data FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE interaction_type = 'click' ORDER BY interaction_time ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM user_interaction_logs GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 100 ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;
SELECT user_id, device_type FROM user_interaction_logs LEFT JOIN user_devices ON user_interaction_logs.user_id = user_devices.user_id WHERE device_type = 'mobile' ORDER BY user_id ASC;

SELECT user_id, AVG(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM interaction_time)) AS avg_interaction_time FROM user_interaction_logs GROUP BY user_id HAVING AVG(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM interaction_time)) > 1600 ORDER BY avg_interaction_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_interaction_logs ORDER BY interaction_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, action_taken FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE device_type = 'Mobile';
SELECT username, email FROM user_profiles WHERE username LIKE 'A%';
SELECT user_id, device_name FROM user_devices WHERE device_name IN ('iPhone', 'Android');
SELECT DISTINCT user_id FROM user_profiles;
SELECT * FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT user_id, interaction_timestamp FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE device_type = 'mobile' ORDER BY interaction_timestamp DESC;
SELECT ui.user_id, ui.action_taken, ud.device_name, up.username FROM user_interaction_logs ui JOIN user_devices ud ON ui.user_id = ud.user_id JOIN user_profiles up ON ui.user_id = up.user_id;
SELECT DISTINCT device_name FROM user_devices;

SELECT up.username, up.email, COUNT(ui.action_taken) AS action_count FROM user_profiles up LEFT JOIN user_interaction_logs ui ON up.user_id = ui.user_id GROUP BY up.username, up.email ORDER BY action_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM UserActions ORDER BY action_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, action_type FROM DeviceInteractions WHERE device_type = 'mobile' ORDER BY action_timestamp ASC;
SELECT user_id, action_type, action_timestamp FROM UserActions WHERE user_id = '12345678-1234-1234-1234-1234567890ab' AND action_timestamp >= '2023-01-01' ORDER BY action_timestamp DESC;
SELECT session_id, user_id, session_start, session_end FROM SessionLogs WHERE user_id = 'abcdef12-3456-7890-abcd-ef1234567890' AND session_start BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-02-01';
SELECT scene_id, interaction_type FROM SceneInteractions WHERE interaction_type = 'click';
SELECT * FROM UserActions ORDER BY action_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, action_type FROM UserActions WHERE action_type = 'login';
SELECT device_id, action_timestamp FROM DeviceInteractions ORDER BY action_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, session_start, session_end FROM SessionLogs WHERE user_id = '1234' ORDER BY session_start DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT scene_id, action_timestamp, interaction_type FROM SceneInteractions WHERE user_id = '5678' AND interaction_type = 'click' ORDER BY action_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_profiles WHERE country = 'USA';
SELECT first_name, last_name, email FROM user_profiles WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY last_name ASC;
SELECT user_id, MAX(age) AS max_age FROM user_profiles GROUP BY user_id HAVING MAX(age) > 21;
SELECT session_id, COUNT(action_id) AS num_actions FROM user_actions GROUP BY session_id ORDER BY num_actions DESC;
SELECT user_id, AVG(age) AS avg_age FROM user_profiles GROUP BY user_id HAVING AVG(age) < 35;
SELECT * FROM user_interaction_logs ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interaction_logs WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;

SELECT user_profiles.first_name, user_profiles.age, user_interaction_logs.interaction_type FROM user_profiles JOIN user_interaction_logs ON user_profiles.user_id = user_interaction_logs.user_id WHERE user_profiles.age > 25 ORDER BY user_interaction_logs.timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM user_interaction_logs GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_interactions > 5 ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;

SELECT user_profiles.first_name, user_devices.device_type, user_actions.action_data FROM user_profiles JOIN user_devices ON user_profiles.user_id = user_devices.user_id JOIN user_sessions ON user_profiles.user_id = user_sessions.user_id JOIN user_actions ON user_sessions.session_id = user_actions.session_id WHERE user_devices.device_type = 'mobile' ORDER BY user_actions.action_id ASC LIMIT 7;
